bar, Arifa (26 May 2017). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/5afdae58-3fe6-11e7-82b6-896b95f30f58\">\"Why I'm No Longer Talking to White People About Race by Reni Eddo-Lodge \u2014 review\"</a>. <i>Financial Times</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Financial+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Why+I%27m+No+Longer+Talking+to+White+People+About+Race+by+Reni+Eddo-Lodge+%E2%80%94+review&amp;rft.date=2017-05-26&amp;rft.au=Akbar%2C+Arifa&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F5afdae58-3fe6-11e7-82b6-896b95f30f58&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWhy+I%27m+No+Longer+Talking+to+White+People+About+Race\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Vi\u00f1as, Silvia (14 November 2017). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.npr.org/2017/11/14/563728725/why-im-no-longer-talking-to-white-people-about-race-is-a-call-to-action\">\"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">'</span>Why I'm No Longer Talking To White People About Race' Is A Call To Action\"</a>. <i>NPR</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=NPR&amp;rft.atitle=%27Why+I%27m+No+Longer+Talking+To+White+People+About+Race%27+Is+A+Call+To+Action&amp;rft.date=2017-11-14&amp;rft.au=Vi%C3%B1as%2C+Silvia&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F563728725%2Fwhy-im-no-longer-talking-to-white-people-about-race-is-a-call-to-action&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWhy+I%27m+No+Longer+Talking+to+White+People+About+Race\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ex